In this folder:

nca:    Building on the altered Express app from the previous recipe, add's custom routes
        using the app.js file and the routes/index.js file
        
nca_route_validation:  Extends nca app to include validation on routes, e.g. route must
                       only contain letters, no numbers or punctuation

nca_optional_routes:  Extends nca app with optional routing, whereby if a route is served
                      whether the placeholder is present or not, so / and /anypage will both
                      trigger the defined route callback

nca_asterisks_globbing:  Extends nca app to utilize the asterisks (*) as a wild card for routes
